T1  - A Theory of the Effects of Advanced Information Technologies on Organizational Design, Intelligence, and Decision Making
AU  - Huber, George P.
Y1  - 1990/01/01
PY  - 1990
DA  - 1990/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1990.4308227
